en_840255_0	Seven people were injured in an accident that took place at the old town of Madampe.
en_840255_1	A Van plying from Kilinochchi to Colombo collided with another Van running from Colombo to Chilaw.
en_840255_2	The injured people were rushed to the Chilaw general hospital.
en_840255_3	Meanwhile, the police have arrested four motorcyclists who had not responded to police command.
en_840255_4	The arrest was made at Watawala.
en_840255_5	According to the police sources, a policeman has received injuries as a motorcyclist had hit and run.
en_840255_6	The suspects were produced before the Hatton Magistrate.
